      "title": "Representatives of Monetary Fund \u2013 Sajith meet",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The representatives of the International Monetary Fund met the Leader of the Opposition yesterday (30) at the Office of the Leader of the Opposition.",
        "It was discussed how to solve the financial crisis that Sri Lanka is currently facing.",
        "The Office of the Leader of the Opposition said that the discussion took place with Peter Breuer, Senior Envoy of the International Monetary Fund for Sri Lanka, Vice President Masahiro Nozaki and Dupakus Perithanushettiavan, Permanent Representative of the International Monetary Fund for Sri Lanka. (a)"
